  "title": "Sales Operation Coordinator (Supply Chain) - Order Processing, Incoterms",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is from a Electronics Manufacturing Industry. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for a Sales Operation Coordinator (Supply Chain) to join their team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the Central area.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits Summary</strong></p><p>• Basic Up $4,300 + Bonuses + Transport Reimbursement Entitlement</p><p>• Office Hours</p><p>• Stable Career Opportunity<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate and liaise with internal teams, suppliers, customers, and freight forwarders to ensure smooth supply chain operations.</li><li>Manage daily shipment arrangements, including purchase order processing, SAP input, scheduling, and checking invoices and delivery documents.</li><li>Support supplier and customer management, including order backlog monitoring, forecast alignment, and relationship management.</li><li>Perform cost analysis and monitor logistics and cargo costs to ensure efficiency and cost-effectiveness.</li><li>May be required to travel occasionally for coordination with stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in logistics / supply chain studies or equivalent.</li><li>Min 3 years’ relevant working experience in logistics, supply chain, or related operations.</li><li>Knowledge of import/export processes, including Incoterms, invoices, and packing lists would be advantageous. </li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint).</li><li>Willing to travel overseas when required.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.<br /></p><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></a><br /></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No. 19C9682</p><p>EA Reg. No. R23115553 (Lai Hor Yan)</p>",
